            <title><![CDATA[Prize Fighter: Heavyweight Edition announced for PS5, PS4]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/prize-fighter-heavyweight-edition-announced-for-ps5-ps4</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/prize-fighter-heavyweight-edition-announced-for-ps5-ps4.1338442/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p><a title="Companies > Screaming Villains [11 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/screaming-villains">Screaming Villains</a> has announced <em><a title="Games > Prize Fighter: Heavyweight Edition" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/prize-fighter-heavyweight-edition">Prize Fighter: Heavyweight Edition</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,726 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a> and <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,490 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>. It will launch in 2026. <span id="more-1003506"></span></p><p><em>Prize Fighter</em> is a <a title="Genres > FMV [14 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/fmv">full-motion video game</a> originally released for <a title="Companies > SEGA [2,713 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sega">SEGA</a> CD in 1993.</p><p>Here is an overview of the game, via the back of its SEGA CD packaging:</p><blockquote><p><strong>About</strong></p><p>This is the main event, Kid!</p><p>Out of of the limo, into the ring, it’s like a movie. But when the bell rings, it’s just you and him! If you’ve got the speed, the muscle, the heart… you might last a round!</p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul><li>Classic boxing <a title="Genres > Action [3,162 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/action">action</a> in TruVideo with realistic, instantaneous control.</li><li>Trainers, cornermen, referees, hecklers…they’ll shout their opinions on your performance.</li><li>Directed by Ron Stein, creator of the boxing sequences in the <em>Rocky</em> movies and <em>Raging Bull</em>.</li><li>You’re “the Kid,” so you won’t get a shot at the Champ ’til you fight your way past three tough hombres.</li><li>Meet your defeat with:<ul><li><strong>Honeyboy Hernandez</strong> – He’s young, he’s green, but he learned what he knows on the street.</li><li><strong>Mega Joe Falco</strong> – A southpaw challenger with lots of experience and skill.</li><li><strong>T. Rex Hawkins</strong> – He’s a real contender, tougher than he looks, and he looks like an industrial machine.</li><li><strong>Nuke “The Duke” Johnson</strong> – The Champeen. Floats like a <a title="Genres > Stealth [101 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/stealth">stealth</a> bomber, stings like a cruise missile.</li></ul></li></ul></blockquote><p>Watch the announcement trailer below.</p><h2><span>Announce Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="LRG3 2025 | 10-Year Anniversary Special" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QK5Ow9zHA4U?start=1940&amp;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/prize-fighter-heavyweight-edition-announced-for-ps5-ps4]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Little Samson coming to PS5, Switch, and PC in 2026]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/little-samson-coming-to-ps5-switch-and-pc-in-2026</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/little-samson-coming-to-ps5-switch-and-pc-in-2026.1338391/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Running on the Carbon Engine.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Limited Run Games [215 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/limited-run-games">Limited Run Games</a> will release <a title="Genres > Side-Scrolling [1,144 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/side-scrolling">side-scrolling</a> <a title="Genres > Action [3,162 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/action">action</a> <a title="Genres > Platformer [776 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/platformer">platformer</a> <em><a title="Games > Little Samson (2026)" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/little-samson-2026">Little Samson</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,726 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,905 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [24,679 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via Steam in 2026, the company announced. It will run on the company’s Carbon Engine. <span id="more-1003500"></span></p><p><em>Little Samson</em>, developed by Takeru and published by <a title="Companies > TAITO [148 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/taito">TAITO</a>, first launched for <a title="Platforms > NES [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/nes">Nintendo Entertainment System</a> on June 26, 1992 in Japan, followed by November 1992 in North America and March 13, 1993 in Europe.</p><p>Here is an overview of the game, via the back of its Nintendo Entertainment System packaging:</p><blockquote><p><strong>About</strong></p><p>The wildest <a title="Genres > Adventure [2,663 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/adventure">adventure</a> of them all!</p><p>The Imperial Forgy has been invaded by Ta-Keed the Prince of Darkness! Only the owners of the Magic Bells can stop his forces from destroying the realm. Led by the mountaineering youth, Samson, a force of unlikely heroes sets out to banish evil forever!</p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p>Become a fire-breathing dragon, a living statue of solid stone or a nimble and crafty mouse! Soar the skies and belch fire balls as Kikira the Dragon Lord! Crush enemy troops with fists of granite as Gamm the Rock Lord. Scurry past dangerous monsters while setting time bombs as K.O. the mouse. These creatures join Little Samson to form a unique and powerful alliance as the last hope for the Imperial Forgy!</p><p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul><li>Incredible graphics bring a new fantasy world to life!</li><li>Battle tactics and game-playing skills are needed to destroy the enemy forces!</li><li>Gain power-ups to build your character’s abilities to unstoppable heights!</li><li>Password feature allows you to return to all the action!</li></ul></blockquote><p>Watch the announcement trailer below.</p><h2><span>Announce Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="LRG3 2025 | 10-Year Anniversary Special" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QK5Ow9zHA4U?start=2049&amp;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/little-samson-coming-to-ps5-switch-and-pc-in-2026]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Slam City with Scottie Pippen: Respect Edition announced for PS5, Xbox Series, PS4, and Switch]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/slam-city-with-scottie-pippen-respect-edition-announced-for-ps5-xbox-series-ps4-and-switch</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/slam-city-with-scottie-pippen-respect-edition-announced-for-ps5-xbox-series-ps4-and-switch.1338388/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p><a title="Companies > Screaming Villains [11 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/screaming-villains">Screaming Villains</a> has announced <em><a title="Games > Slam City with Scottie Pippen: Respect Edition" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/slam-city-with-scottie-pippen-respect-edition">Slam City with Scottie Pippen: Respect Edition</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,726 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,205 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,490 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, and <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,905 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>. It will launch in 2026. <span id="more-1003503"></span></p><p><em>Slam City with Scottie Pippen</em> is a <a title="Genres > FMV [14 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/fmv">full-motion video game</a> first released for <a title="Companies > SEGA [2,713 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sega">SEGA</a> CD, SEGA CD 32X, and MS-DOS in November 1994.</p><p>Here is an overview of the game, via the back of its SEGA CD 32X packaging:</p><blockquote><p><strong>About</strong></p><p>This ain’t no cartoon game. This is where real basketball is played… by real players on the street! Of you can beat these guys and earn enough respect, you actually get to take on Scottie Pippen!</p><p>Slam City has all the <a title="Genres > Action [3,162 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/action">action</a> of real one-on-one basketball. You can shoot or drive to the hoop. You can steal the ball or block shots. It’s all in there. You got the rock. Now take it to the hole.</p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul><li>A real interactive movie, not a computer-generated game.</li><li>Perform spectacular live-action moves to the hoop!</li><li>Go one-on-one with five of the slammin’est hoopsters on the blacktop:<ul><li><strong>Fingers</strong> – He talks a lot of trash. He has to look good when he scores.</li><li><strong>Juice</strong> – She can hit anything from anywhere. Competition is her middle name; makin’ you look bad is her game.</li><li><strong>Mad Dog</strong> – He’s been known to ask for help climbing off the backboard after skying past you to the hoop. White men can jump.</li><li><strong>Smash</strong> – He’s from the same gene pool as the big men. Hates humanity. Hates you.</li><li><strong>Scottie Pippen</strong> – The real thing-not some cheap cartoon character that maybe on a good day sorta looks like him. There ain’t nobody tougher.</li></ul></li></ul></blockquote><p>Watch the announcement trailer below.</p><h2><span>Announce Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="LRG3 2025 | 10-Year Anniversary Special" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QK5Ow9zHA4U?start=1681&amp;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/slam-city-with-scottie-pippen-respect-edition-announced-for-ps5-xbox-series-ps4-and-switch]]></content:encoded>
